title: Exception thrown when exporting data from table containing highlight/map
description: Description: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from the attached report.
OB: When exporting data from a table that contains a group, a highlight rule, and a map rule in the group row, an exception is thrown.
SR: To reproduce the issue:  1. Add a table to the report that has a group, a highlight rule, and a map rule in the group row.  2. Preview the report.  3. Attempt to export the data from the table.
